history.content:
On March 12, 2021, CITRIS, AWE, and the Women in Tech Initiative at UC will be hosting the Women in Tech Symposium on Human-Computer Interaction (HCI).

 

This event also includes a FREE career fair from 4pm - 6pm PT. Students can meet with recruiters, engineers, designers, and researchers from leading tech companies and graduate programs to get connected with exciting career opportunities in HCI, UI/UX and more!

Career Fair Registration: http://wit2021.eventbrite.com/
